title: Rock / Roll - A Squirrelhead Compilation
description:
A friend of mine, SquirrelHead, made a compilation for me back in high school that I loved. Finally ripped it and then re-grabbed all of the songs -- no small feat. Also included are soundbytes galore. Take yourself back to the old 90-minute cassette days and enjoy:
